---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="DevOps & Cloud | Jay Software - Scale Without Breaking Your Budget"
  description="Stop losing $25K+/month to infrastructure problems. Bulletproof cloud solutions that reduce costs 40-60%, guarantee 99.9% uptime, and auto-scale with your growth."
  keywords="DevOps services, cloud infrastructure, AWS consulting, Azure consulting, Google Cloud, cloud migration, CI/CD pipelines, container orchestration, cloud cost optimization"
  canonicalUrl="https://jay-software.com/services/devops-cloud"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-900/20 to-blue-900/20 border-b border-slate-700">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-cyan-600/20 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-cyan-300 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
            ☁️ DevOps & Cloud
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Stop Losing <span class="text-red-400">$25K+/Month</span> to
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              Infrastructure Problems
            </span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Bulletproof cloud infrastructure that scales automatically, reduces costs by 40-60%, and eliminates downtime. Built for growth, not problems.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/#strategic-consultation" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 to-blue-600 hover:from-cyan-700 hover:to-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
              Get Infrastructure Audit
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problems Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Is Your Infrastructure <span class="text-red-400">Bleeding Money</span>?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            Poor DevOps and cloud setup costs businesses thousands monthly in downtime, security issues, and inefficiency...
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">💥</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Constant Downtime</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Server crashes, slow deployments, and unreliable infrastructure costing revenue and reputation.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">💸</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Sky-High Cloud Bills</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Unoptimized cloud resources eating into profits with unnecessary compute and storage costs.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🐌</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Slow Deployments</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Manual deployment processes taking hours or days, slowing down business growth.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🚨</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Security Vulnerabilities</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Unpatched systems, misconfigured security, and compliance issues putting business at risk.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">📊</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">No Monitoring</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Blind spots in system performance leading to issues discovered by customers, not you.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">⚖️</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Scaling Nightmares</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Infrastructure that breaks under load, preventing business growth and costing opportunities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
